snippet.title: Mexico, 1921: A Deep Slumber - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
🚨🇲🇽Mexico, 1921: A Deep Slumber has a release date! 

Discover post revolutionary Mexico through the eyes of  a photojournalist that will discover that Mexico ain't no place for the weak! 

Coming to Steam September 13th, 2024.
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1851090/Mexico_1921_A_Deep_Slumber/
